1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY

CVSS v3 7.5
ATTENTION: Exploitable remotely/low attack complexity 
Vendor: Siemens 
Equipment: SCALANCE X200 IRT Products 
Vulnerability: Improper Input Validation 

2. RISK EVALUATION
